<p><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: 0;">Hemen ne demek istedi</span><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: 0;">ğ</span><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: 0;">imi a</span><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: 0;">&ccedil;</span><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: 0;">ay</span><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: 0;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: 0;">m. Yaz seyircisi ile k</span><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: 0;">ış </span><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: 0;">seyircisi aras</span><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: 0;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: 0;">nda b</span><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: 0;">&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: 0;">y</span><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: 0;">&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: 0;">k fark vard</span><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: 0;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: 0;">r. Yaz seyircisi </span><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: 0;">&ccedil;ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: 0;">t</span><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: 0;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: 0;">r </span><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: 0;">&ccedil;</span><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: 0;">erez a</span><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: 0;">ş</span><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: 0;">k hikayesi sever; k</span><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: 0;">ış </span><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: 0;">seyircisi soru sorduran, cevap pe</span><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: 0;">ş</span><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: 0;">inde ko</span><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: 0;">ş</span><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: 0;">turan netameli hikayeleri. Yaz seyircisi; Ali ile Selin, Sava</span><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: 0;