<p><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: 0;">Na</span><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: 0;">&ccedil;</span><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: 0;">izane g</span><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: 0;">&ouml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: 0;">r</span><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: 0;">&uuml;ş&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: 0;">m, hikayenin </span><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: 0;">ş</span><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: 0;">u </span><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: 0;">&uuml;&ccedil; </span><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: 0;">haftal</span><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: 0;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: 0;">k s</span><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: 0;">&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: 0;">re i</span><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: 0;">&ccedil;</span><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: 0;">erisinde Haluk ve onun etraf</span><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: 0;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: 0;">na toplanmas</span><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: 0;">ı </span><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: 0;">laz</span><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: 0;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: 0;">m. Haluk, G</span><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: 0;">&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: 0;">ne</span><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: 0;">ş</span><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: 0;">, R</span><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: 0;">&acirc;</span><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: 0;">n</span><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: 0;">&acirc;</span><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: 0;">, Sevilay, Ahmet ve onun kafadan kontak kar</span><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: 0;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: 0